<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Rickmansworth | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Rickmansworth. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Rickmansworth and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:340px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(3).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 48px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Rickmansworth</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,52px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Plasterer in Rickmansworth</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">WD3 · Plastering, rendering &amp; decorating across Rickmansworth and the Chess Valley.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">About Rickmansworth</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">A market town on the Three Rivers — Victorian and Edwardian centre, executive homes along the Chess and Colne valleys.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Rickmansworth's historic town centre has period commercial and residential stock. The surrounding villages — Chorleywood Road, Croxley Green, Moor Park — contain a mix of 1930s suburban development and high-value detached properties. Plastering and rendering are consistent across all types. The executive homes in Moor Park and along the Golf Course corridors drive demand for high-end finishes.</p>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">We're based in Harefield, making Rickmansworth a straightforward drive via the A404. Watford is accessible on the same run.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Common problems</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">What goes wrong in Rickmansworth's housing stock.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Period plaster in the town centre</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The Victorian and Edwardian stock in the old town has solid walls and lime plaster — it needs breathable, compatible repair, not a modern gypsum patch that traps moisture.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Render maintenance on the villages</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Croxley Green, Moor Park, and the Chorleywood Road properties carry rendered elevations that weather and need periodic patch repair and repainting.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Damp on low-lying properties</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The Three Rivers setting means some properties near the Chess, Gade, and Colne sit at a higher damp exposure, which can drive plaster failure on ground-floor walls.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Neighbourhoods we work in</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">A market town where three rivers meet.</h2>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Rickmansworth's historic centre carries Victorian and Edwardian commercial and residential stock. The surrounding villages each have their own character — <strong>Croxley Green</strong> with its mix of interwar suburban and high-value homes, <strong>Moor Park</strong> with its substantial executive properties along the golf-course corridors, and the Chorleywood Road approaches. The Metropolitan line and the M25 keep it well connected.</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Plastering and rendering are consistent across all of it, with the Moor Park stock driving demand for higher-end finishes.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What homeowners ask for</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Plastering, rendering, and high-end finishes.</h2>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">The mix spans plastering and re-skims, exterior render and masonry painting, and — in Moor Park especially — Venetian plastering and premium interior decorating. Period repair features in the town centre. Exterior work is planned around dry conditions.</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">A clear written quote and a fixed price agreed before we start, whatever the spec.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Rickmansworth</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">~20 minutes from base</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">A straightforward drive from Harefield via the A404. A regular working area — Watford is on the same run.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">High-spec ready</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">From standard render work to Venetian plaster in Moor Park — we bring the right materials and finish for the property.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Period-aware</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Town-centre period walls get breathable, compatible repair. We assess before specifying.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Clean, tidy, insured</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Surfaces protected, site left tidy daily. Fully insured, City &amp; Guilds qualified, no subcontractors.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
